<h3 style=”text-align:left”><b><u>Chris Taylor</u></b></h3><img src="9.jpg" align="right" width="250" length="250"/>
<p>Full Name: Christopher Peter Taylor</p>
<p>Born: September 14, 1988, Shepparton</p>
<p>Nicknames: Tay</p>
<p>Batting style: Left-hand bat</p>
<p>Bowling style: Left-arm medium fast</p>
<p>Fielding position: Mid-off, mid-on, occasional wicketkeeper</p>
<p>Teams: Shepparton United, Glenroy, Willowfest</p>
<p>Shirt number: 33</p>
<p>Relations: Father - <a href="10.php">Doug Taylor</a>, Brother - <a href="77.php">Damien Taylor</a>, Brother - <a href="18.php">Andrew Taylor</a></p>
<a href="halloffame.php"><img src="halloffame.jpg" length="100" width="100" border="0"/></a>
